<taxonomicName id="4C0FFDD69151FFEDE7D1C2482B1DABFE" baseAuthorityName="Wagner" baseAuthorityYear="1843" box="[931,1100,2923,2956]" class="Mammalia" family="Mormoopidae" genus="Pteronotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="440" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="personatus">P. personatus</taxonomicName>
, but here it is considered a distinct species. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
